<html>
<head>
	<meta content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href=":/resources/cheatsheet/cheatsheet.css" type="text/css" />
</head>

<body>
	<h1>Agglomeration</h1>

	<p><a href=#annotation_seg>Segmentation table view</a> | <a href=#pref_seg>Visibility preferences</a></p>
	<p><a href=#navi>Navigation preferences</a></p>

	<p>
	Segmentation mode for proofreading of agglomeration. KNOSSOS streams segmentation and 3D models from a server and automatically uploads work.
	</p>

	<p>
	<table>
		<thead>
			<tr><th align="left"><h3>Shortcut</h3></th><th align="left"><h3>Action</h3></th></tr>
			<tr><th colspan="2" align="left">Navigation</th></tr>
		</thead>
		<tr><td><span class="sh"><img src=":/resources/cheatsheet/leftclick.png" alt="Left click"/></span></td><td>Select object</td></tr>
		<tr><td><span class="sh">S</span></td><td>Jump to clicked location in work object or reselect it</td></tr>
		<tr><td><span class="sh">B</span></td><td>Place branchpoint at hovered position</td></tr>
		<tr><td><span class="sh">J</span></td><td>Jump to last branchpoint</td></tr>
		<thead>
			<tr><th colspan="2" align="left"><hr>Merging & Splitting in 2D</th></tr>
		</thead>
		<tr><td><span class="sh"><img src=":/resources/cheatsheet/rightclick.png" alt="Right click"/> drag</span></td><td>Merge objects</td></tr>
		<tr><td><span class="sh">Shift + <img src=":/resources/cheatsheet/rightclick.png" alt="Right click"/> drag</span></td><td>Quick split objects</td></tr>
		<thead>
			<tr><th colspan="2" align="left"><hr>Split Mode</th></tr>
		</thead>
		<tr><td colspan="2">Unlike quick split, split mode works in all viewports.</td>

		<tr><td><span class="sh">Shift + <img src=":/resources/cheatsheet/rightclick.png" alt="Right click"/> on target</span></td><td>Enter split mode for target object</td></tr>
		<tr><td><span class="sh"><img src=":/resources/cheatsheet/rightclick.png" alt="Right click"/> on other</span></td><td>Split off from target</td></tr>
		<tr><th colspan="2"><hr></th></tr>
		<tr><td><span class="sh">Ctrl + Z</span></td><td>Undo merge or split</td></tr>
		<thead>
			<tr><th colspan="2" align="left"><hr>Visibility</th></tr>
		</thead>
		<tr><td><span class="sh">Ctrl + <img src=":/resources/cheatsheet/middleclick.png" alt="Wheel"/> scroll</span></td><td>Zoom</td></tr>
		<tr><td><span class="sh">Ctrl + 0</span></td><td>Zoom reset</td></tr>
		<tr><td><span class="sh">+</span></td><td>Increase segmentation opacity</td></tr>
		<tr><td><span class="sh">-</span></td><td>Decrease segmentation opacity</td></tr>
		<tr><td><span class="sh">Hold space</span></td><td>Hide segmentation overlay temporarily</td></tr>
	</table>
	</p>
</body>
</html>
